coins.notes: Multiple design variations: No Stars (1837-1838), Stars (1838-1860), Legend (1860-1891).
coins.obverse_description: Liberty seated on rock, holding shield with 'LIBERTY' and pole with liberty cap, 13 stars around, date below
coins.reverse_description: Wreath encircling 'ONE DIME', 'UNITED STATES OF AMERICA' around
